General.Name: Staatl. Mineralbrunnen AG
General.Description: Staatl. Mineralbrunnen AG produces and distributes mineral water and soft drinks in Germany. The company offers medicinal water, spritzers, and gourmets. It also sells its products online. The company was founded in 1747 and is based in Bad Brückenau, Germany.
